og.description: Nebraska and Creighton both earned national seeds on the road to Omaha in the NCAA volleyball tournament. The Huskers earned a top 4 seed, while the Bluejays earned the final national seed, No. 16. Omaha hosts the final four on Dec. 17 and 19 at the CenturyLink Center.
